0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Religious conservatives from around the world decried the segment, with the French Catholic Church's conference of bishops deploring \\\"scenes of derision\\\" that they said made a mockery of Christianity - a sentiment echoed by Russian Foreign Ministry spokesperson Maria Zakharova.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 956, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999998899361405, \"rank\": 7.606085681978935e-08, \"text\": \"Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 1067, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9987782471750871, \"rank\": 0.0012231081786841331, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 1104, \"end\": 1128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\", \"score\": 0.9999999998756266, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Russian Foreign Ministry\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_(Russia)\"}, {\"begin\": 1142, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maria Zakharova\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maria_Zakharova\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Anglican Communion in Egypt expressed its \\\"deep regret\\\" Sunday, saying the ceremony could cause the IOC to \\\"lose its distinctive sporting identity and its humanitarian message.\\\"\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1340, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1163, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anglican_Communion\", \"score\": 0.999355087294464, \"rank\": 0.0006453288863417266, \"text\": \"Anglican Communion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anglican_Communion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anglican_Communion\"}, {\"begin\": 1185, \"end\": 1190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"score\": 0.9999977154844775, \"rank\": 1.8977993470233977e-06, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\"}, {\"begin\": 1263, \"end\": 1266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.548217158493677e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony's artistic director Thomas Jolly had distanced his scene from any \\\"Last Supper\\\" parallels after the ceremony, saying it was meant to celebrate diversity and pay tribute to feasting and French gastronomy.\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9999965174771819, \"rank\": 3.3185680227179592e-06, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\