\"to\": 1888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1874, \"end\": 1882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking at the result of the polls that we shared, we believe that this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offense we are, of course, really, really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jolly explained his intentions to The Associated Press after the ceremony.\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2099, \"end\": 2115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9978006139537667, \"rank\": 0.002204234007653125, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My wish is not to be subversive, nor to mock or to shock,\\\" Jolly said.\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most of all, I wanted to send a message of love, a message of inclusion and not at all to divide.\\\"\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2308, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Associated Press journalist Samy Magdy contributed reporting from Cairo.\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2310, \"end\": 2326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9978006139537667, \"rank\": 0.002204234007653125, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\